Class UGEdge<Value extends UGNodeInterface>

    public class UGEdge<Value extends UGNodeInterface>
extends java.lang.Object
    All comments are done in english, because, programming... This class represents an edge in the Undirected Graph It keeps track of which pair of vertices it is connected to, and has a float value for its weight
